DOC.brief_summary: This study will evaluate the effectiveness of OnabotulinumtoxinA to prevent headaches in patients with Chronic Migraine.
DOC.brief_title: A Retrospective Study to Evaluate the Effectiveness of onabotulinumtoxinA in Preventing Headaches in Patients With Chronic Migraines
DOC.criteria: History of chronic migraines 15 or more headache days over a 30 day period A minimum of 2 consecutive treatment cycles of 100 units onabotulinumtoxinA and a minimum of 2 consecutive treatment cycles with the onabotulinumtoxinA dosing between 155 and 195 units Any treatment cycle dose of onabotulinumtoxinA greater than 200 units
